      "content": "yo, im running a detective rpg session for some friends and need help setting the scene. the crime happened in a part of the city thats pretty rough—lots of boarded up shops, graffiti everywhere, some crumbling apartment complexes, and basically just a high-poverty area where people are struggling. if my detective is walking through there looking for a suspect who might have done a robbery, what kind of person or profile should they realistically be looking for based on that kind of neighborhood?",
